name: Nibnaks
overview:
NiBNAKS is a newly launched startup , offers a healthy solution to snacking in the workplace.

NiBNAKS is a way for employers to offer healthy alternatives to the traditional unhealthy vending machine snacks that are prominent in many workplaces. While many traditional snacks are high in sugar content, NiBNAKS focuses on portion-controlled snacks that encourage grazing on natural foods. Corporate clients interested in re-fueling their employees with nutritious treats can get more information by going to the website, http://www.nibnaks.com. On the site, individual users can also sign up to order snack mixes as per their own preferences and tastes. Founded in 2012, NiBNAKS is based in Palo Alto, CA.
